Artificially high turnover between low richness communities

Ruan van Mazijk

13 April 2018

source("turnover_across_richness.R")

Max community richness \(\approx\) regional richness

turnover_across_richness(100, 100)

turnover_across_richness(500, 500)

Max community richness \(\lt\) regional richness

Regional richness = 1000

turnover_across_richness(750, 1000)

turnover_across_richness(500, 1000)

turnover_across_richness(250, 1000)

turnover_across_richness(100, 1000)

Regional richness = 500

turnover_across_richness(500, 500)

turnover_across_richness(250, 500)

turnover_across_richness(50, 500)

Regional richness = 100

turnover_across_richness(75, 100)

turnover_across_richness(50, 100)

turnover_across_richness(25, 100)

turnover_across_richness(10, 100)
